Title: dateName
Description: date_part — Date part. Possible values: 'year', 'quarter', 'month', 'week', 'dayofyear', 'day', 'weekday', 'hour', 'minute', 'second'. String.date — Date. Date, Date32, DateTime or DateTime64.timezone — Timezone. Optional. String.
The specified part of date. String
Examples: WITH toDateTime('2021-04-14 11:22:33') AS date_valueSELECT    dateName('year', date_value),    dateName('month', date_value),    dateName('day', date_value);
